{"tid":513760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呈40人求情信包括曾偉雄 朱經緯求判社服令 還柙過年　下周三判刑","createTime":"2017-12-30T01:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T04:01:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"afd9c4ce0b80043626f9d9ce55332a3308455753","tid":513760,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:23:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171230/20259783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F20259783&d=aM7vva%2FQTNmAI2Cu%2Fh29Sb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=663faeeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F20259783&h=225b6fd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171230/20259783</a><br />\n<br />\n呈40人求情信包括曾偉雄<br />\n朱經緯求判社服令<br />\n還柙過年　下周三判刑<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】退休警司朱經緯傘運期間以警棍擊傷途人，早前罪成還柙候判，在獄中度聖誕及生日。案件原定昨宣判，朱獲曾偉雄及鄧竟成兩名前一哥撰求情信，另有近40人求情，包括退休副處長、助理處長及立法會議員。辯方盼法庭按照感化官建議判處社會服務令，甚至緩刑，惟辯方庭上未有指朱有悔意或向事主致歉。主任裁判官錢禮需時考慮求情信及報告內容，押後判刑至明年1月3日，下令朱繼續還柙。朱要在獄中跨年。<br />\n<br />\n記者：楊家樂　歐陽聯發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171230/large/30la1p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171230%2Flarge%2F30la1p1.jpg&h=14f2f848&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱經緯昨早被鎖上手銬，乘囚車到法庭應訊。<br />\n謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n被告朱經緯昨早由囚車押送到庭，等候下午判刑。朱略見憔悴，表情肅穆，目光銳利。當錢官步出法庭時他未有鞠躬，獲准坐下時亦未向錢官致謝。其後錢官宣佈押後判刑，朱的代表大狀彭彼得欲繼續陳詞，但未及出聲，錢官已即時下令朱繼續還柙。散庭後有旁聽人士大叫：「咁保釋呢？」已返回羈留室的朱向彭招手示意，但隔空來回數句後，彭搖搖頭，朱亦被庭警帶走。據曾探監人士透露，朱在獄中精神不錯。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指案發實屬不幸<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指，朱返教會30年，今年聖誕未能與家人共聚實屬遺憾，更要獨自在獄中過生日，不禁問為何落得如此下場，朱要以這種形式結束警隊生涯，已是最大懲罰。辯方強調朱是教徒、忠誠的公僕、好友、好爸爸以及兩個女人的好丈夫，今次案發實屬不幸。朱由事發至被捕歷經2年4個月，到定罪更達3年1個月，延誤甚久，一家身心俱疲。<br />\n辯方又呈上40封求情信，直指其中包括兩名前警務處處長，以及多名退休副處長和助理處長，盡皆證明朱獻身警隊，多年來服務社會，盡忠職守，表現卓越，並曾獲特首及公務員事務局嘉許。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，兩名前一哥分別是在9.28催淚彈清場行動後向前線人員高呼「你哋冇做錯到」的曾偉雄，及曾就警隊執法問題向公眾道歉而被戲稱為「Sorry Sir」的鄧竟成。上次及今次也有到庭的退休刑事及保安處處長羅夢熊亦有寫求情信。<br />\n<br />\n另外，香港警司協會及香港警務督察協會分別寫信聲援朱，其中後者主席更表示會毫無保留支持朱，辯方指可見全港警員支持朱的說法有根有據。當中有人揚言朱當時臨近退休，大可向警方申請不參與行動，但朱仍堅持走到最前線，令人欽佩。<br />\n<br />\n此外，朱不但在港訓練警員，亦曾代表本港到澳門訓練執法人員，獲當地治安警察局及海關撰信支持。4名本港立法會議員、包括葉劉淑儀亦有撰寫求情信，他們均與朱相識。而的士前線司機總會及的士司機從業員總會亦有求情。<br />\n<br />\n辯方再次覆述案情，指案發當日現場聚集500、600人，狀況瞬息萬變，朱可能判斷錯誤，但大眾不能事後孔明指摘他，而警例的確賦予警員酌情權使用武力，朱只為執勤，並非為打人。朱受上級指示，不容群眾再佔據彌敦道與亞皆老街交界路面，加上經歷長時間佔領運動，為保亞洲最佳警隊聲譽，壓力甚大。<br />\n<br />\n辯方更將矛頭指向事主鄭仲恒，揚言他根本不應留在現場，質疑他是運動中活躍分子。錢官質疑案中根本沒證據指鄭是衝擊者，更何況法庭已裁定鄭是途人。辯方遂謂最重要是被告覺得事主是衝擊者之一，才會使用武力，並非漫無目的地打人。現在朱既已退休，重犯機會已不存在。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC1912/17<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171230/large/a0201a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171230%2Flarge%2Fa0201a.gif&h=e192dc04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t朱被稱「好老公」官：不是已離婚嗎？<br />\n要聞 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t被告倘無真誠悔意　或不獲判社服令<br />\n要聞 4小時前"},{"pid":"fb7ba52ec7354856142fa71e6c92d757666fa4d4","tid":513760,"uid":51127,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:28:23.000Z","msg":"睇佢個仔就知佢地到今日都未知自己錯乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3983a3c14084fc014f094067c8679f56e6f28d0","tid":513760,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fb7ba52ec7354856142fa71e6c92d757666fa4d4","tid":513760,"uid":51127,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:28:23.000Z","msg":"睇佢個仔就知佢地到今日都未知自己錯乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:41:14.000Z","msg":"呀sir做野唔洗你教"},{"pid":"71e15eeb0e7ee0d825a53daeb082eb8c140a39da","tid":513760,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:45:57.000Z","msg":"判硬社令"},{"pid":"c4d81ed2c64704bdd5201b91982d6a8b7d5c444b","tid":513760,"uid":59536,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:47:14.000Z","msg":"兩個女人的好丈夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404e98265b6dceb1d18da220108302e558b6cb93","tid":513760,"uid":51127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:47:22.000Z","msg":"豬sir 肯道個歉，個官就唔駛咁難做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe8efe635e0205077862bb62b6d209463150fbb","tid":513760,"uid":2613,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:47:27.000Z","msg":"教徒、忠誠的公僕、好友、好爸爸以及兩個女人的好丈夫<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85709a6ba12d98828a5a4fdc46684a93c0ab5e8c","tid":513760,"uid":51127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfe8efe635e0205077862bb62b6d209463150fbb","tid":513760,"uid":2613,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:47:27.000Z","msg":"教徒、忠誠的公僕、好友、好爸爸以及兩個女人的好丈夫<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:49:29.000Z","msg":"齊人之福<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501812b684eeb9b1cf8d760e887a8eb5105acdfa","tid":513760,"uid":72990,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"黃c不嬲打得少<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持朱蛇"},{"pid":"71e42c51c10b2ef93387c481ecf8b16bc9765691","tid":513760,"uid":160916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71e15eeb0e7ee0d825a53daeb082eb8c140a39da","tid":513760,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:45:57.000Z","msg":"判硬社令"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T01:59:08.000Z","msg":"個官係咁串佢睇黎佢都好唔妥個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">犯人</span></span><br />\n有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c7c8133f89abb059494805868696a866cf0b76","tid":513760,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:20:35.000Z","msg":"判一個月但收押期已經夠數,所以當庭釋放<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a6727f454daae4ffeab142fc3c43d402c7c0c7","tid":513760,"uid":132238,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:23:21.000Z","msg":"成件事最搞笑既地方係連做下樣扮有悔意都唔肯，唔通當時一哥話&ldquo;你地冇做錯到！&rdquo;就真係做乜都得咩<br />\n<br />\n就算當時朱sir誤判受害人係佔中活躍份子並基於合理情況下出手打人，係法庭已裁定被打條友係路過，純粹不幸意外既前提下，起碼都say個sorry啦<br />\n<br />\n以為有人撐就門面野都唔做，俾人拉你入獄過年就抵死啦"},{"pid":"baadbe4e7cae8bee9b46633caed4d292cddde4df","tid":513760,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:26:20.000Z","msg":"上到咁高位<br />\n條頸硬過鋼板<br />\n點會認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e1296913c0db297047cd6bfce3bc5b7004498d","tid":513760,"uid":11890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:31:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 朱由事發至被捕歷經2年4個月，到定罪更達3年1個月，延誤甚久，一家身心俱疲。</blockquote><br />\n執法部門一路死拖爛拖唔做嘢拉人<br />\n你一路大安旨意退休享福<br />\n有乜撚咁身心俱疲呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5def11df9420f218ea0f802ee531afbf66be2b","tid":513760,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T02:31:36.000Z","msg":"兩個女人的好丈夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e11a4a8baa0401b8800e662dc6e41726a84af2","tid":513760,"uid":13674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"咁唔尊重個官 <br />\n仲要無d悔意<br />\n比我係個官求情最多坐少d"},{"pid":"9f59bc30ad889c395e7d46ee6f8b75116bb595f2","tid":513760,"uid":38540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:17:27.000Z","msg":"今年聖誕未能與家人共聚實屬遺憾，更要獨自在獄中過生日，不禁問為何落得如此下場<br />\n<br />\n睇見都嬲 仲問點解落得如此下場 死黑警 估中個陣啲畫面返哂黎 好撚心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好獄中過年 年年有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e021c93a91b2efb241e4a323b1a02c0f9f55c59f","tid":513760,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:20:47.000Z","msg":"的士佬都幫寫求情信<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8975e1fd729ee5bb9440dc059897f58e43dd932a","tid":513760,"uid":5971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e021c93a91b2efb241e4a323b1a02c0f9f55c59f","tid":513760,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:20:47.000Z","msg":"的士佬都幫寫求情信<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"睇到眼都突埋"},{"pid":"d60910163469e3f9b77be9891d9c16901247bf85","tid":513760,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:30:04.000Z","msg":"關澳門乜事啊？<br />\n咁都要寫求情信？"},{"pid":"13fb1fb17b70f034bfcf8a19189ddf890256bfee","tid":513760,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e021c93a91b2efb241e4a323b1a02c0f9f55c59f","tid":513760,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:20:47.000Z","msg":"的士佬都幫寫求情信<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T04:01:04.000Z","msg":"你唔明嫁啦，平時抄牌既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a883edfc95c7c2398f41189e6f253c0d63c2a2fd","tid":513760,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s